            </ab></div>
            <div type="translation" source="#tantillo2010" xml:lang="it">
                <p>Per la salvezza dei nostri signori! Flavius Lucretius Florentinus Rusticus, uomo perfettissimo, governatore, collocò.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" source="#lsa" xml:lang="en">
                <p>For the safety of our lords. Flavius Lucretius Florentinus Rusticus, of perfectissimus rank, governor (<foreign xml:lang="la">praeses</foreign>), set this here.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                
                <p>Fl. Lucretius Florentinus Rusticus: <title>PLRE</title> I, Rusticus 1.</p>
